fields.title: Request for Approval – Intern Stipends and Travel Allowance
fields.description:
Requesting approval for financial provisions for five interns who made valuable contributions to the JN Central Library, extending their initial one-month internship to three months due to their excellent work.
Specifically, we request:
 * Rs. 4,000 each for four hosteler interns (Abhinand, Midhlaj, Mufitha, Sayana).
 * Rs. 6,000 travel allowance for one non-hosteler intern (Haseeba).
Approving this will highly encourage these dedicated individuals.
